{"tid":1545631,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[ONE IT] PRODUCE_X101及X1討論區 (115) 等左成朝都冇人開po...","createTime":"2019-09-06T03:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:07:56.000Z","uid":62035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc111e2f5d02ab52fa0eab0bbe46395b3694fc9","tid":1545631,"uid":62035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>歡迎各位連登製作人<br />\n你可以係度發表有關PRODUCE X 101所有練習生及組合X1既意見<br />\n最重要互相尊重 一齊維持良好和諧既氣氛</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>X1<br />\n엑스원</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>9.01 X1首個一位！<br />\n9.02 專輯首周銷量突破50萬張！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">FLASH MV</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LlQEKB2H7z4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLlQEKB2H7z4&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=0e128dcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LlQEKB2H7z4</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EC_CBnwX4AE3Elx?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEC_CBnwX4AE3Elx%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=8412e1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ECWDq7VU4AEcTKe?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FECWDq7VU4AEcTKe%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=7ffb813e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ECWI9LzUYAAw6tQ?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FECWI9LzUYAAw6tQ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=79e2304e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EAFayYTUcAAMayL?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEAFayYTUcAAMayL%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=6fa1219e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZqHWGh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZqHWGh.png&h=41ebf68d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nX1（韓語：엑스원 X Won）是由Mnet選秀節目《PRODUCE X 101》的出道承諾，由最終決選出線的11名成員所組成，於2019年成立的韓國男子音樂組合，成員名單以投票方式決定。成員依排名為金曜漢、金宇碩、韓勝宇、宋亨俊、曹承衍、孫東杓、李翰潔、南道賢、車俊昊、姜敏熙、李垠尚。<br />\n<br />\n2019年整體以SWING娛樂旗下藝人身份出道（各自則有所屬的經紀公司），由SWING娛樂管理團體合約，CJ E&amp;M負責音樂製作，團體活動限定5年，前2.5年為專屬合約，後2.5年可於原公司進行活動。<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月27日以首張迷你專輯《飛翔:QUANTUM LEAP》主打曲《FLASH》正式出道，並在首爾高尺天空巨蛋舉辦出道SHOW-CON。官方粉絲名為「ONE IT」(원잇)。<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月22日播放首個團綜《X1 FLASH》。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">要安俊英年早逝？<br />\n唔洗用劍嘅！<br />\n用李鎭赫旋風夠晒威<br />\n赫旋風的確好洗！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qxZZe8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qxZZe8.gif&h=0833c36d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCr to 藍色女人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>正名更好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>之參賽者花名表</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/1urtD3aMQ76E5zpYMJAjGKMJEmGWJZAGw_v_VXOlMZ6w/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fu%2F1%2Fd%2F1urtD3aMQ76E5zpYMJAjGKMJEmGWJZAGw_v_VXOlMZ6w%2Fhtmlview&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=43503095\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/1urtD3aMQ76E5zpYMJAjGKMJEmGWJZAGw_v_VXOlMZ6w/